### Get All Bookings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings

### Add Booking 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-05-01",
  "endDate": "2025-05-05",
  "totalCost": 250.00,
  "confirmed": true,
  "linkedCustomer": { "id": 1 }
}

### Add Booking 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-06-10",
  "endDate": "2025-06-15",
  "totalCost": 400.00,
  "confirmed": false,
  "linkedCustomer": { "id": 2 }
}

### Search Booking by username
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/search?username=john_doe

### Delete Booking
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/1